color:black'>Those interested in organizing a workshop at ICLP 2012 are inv=
ited
to<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal><span style=3D'font-size:10.0pt;font-family:"Courier N=
ew";
color:black'>submit a workshop proposal. Proposals should be in English and
about<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal><span style=3D'font-size:10.0pt;font-family:"Courier N=
ew";
color:black'>two pages in length. They should contain:<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal><span style=3D'font-size:10.0pt;font-family:"Courier N=
ew";
color:black'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal><span style=3D'font-size:10.0pt;font-family:"Courier N=
ew";
color:black'>&nbsp;* The title of the workshop.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal><span style=3D'font-size:10.0pt;font-family:"Courier N=
ew";
color:black'>&nbsp;* A brief technical description of the topics covered by=
 the
workshop.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal><span style=3D'font-size:10.0pt;font-family:"Courier N=
ew";
color:black'>&nbsp;* A discussion of the timeliness and relevance of the
workshop.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal><span style=3D'font-size:10.0pt;font-family:"Courier N=
ew";
color:black'>&nbsp;* A list of some related workshops held in the last year=
s<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal><span style=3D'font-size:10.0pt;font-family:"Courier N=
ew";
color:black'>&nbsp;* The requested number of half-days allotted to the work=
shop<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal><span style=3D'font-size:10.0pt;font-family:"Courier N=
ew";
color:black'>&nbsp;&nbsp; and an estimate of the number of expected attende=
es.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal><span style=3D'font-size:10.0pt;font-family:"Courier N=
ew";
color:black'>&nbsp;* The names, affiliation and contact details (email, web
page,<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal><span style=3D'font-size:10.0pt;font-family:"Courier N=
ew";
color:black'>&nbsp;&nbsp; phone) of the workshop organizers together with a
designated<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal><span style=3D'font-size:10.0pt;font-family:"Courier N=
ew";
color:black'>&nbsp;&nbsp; contact person.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal><span style=3D'font-size:10.0pt;font-family:"Courier N=
ew";
color:black'>&nbsp;* Previous experience of the workshop organizers in<o:p>=
</o:p></span></p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal><span style=3D'font-size:10.0pt;font-family:"Courier N=
ew";
color:black'>&nbsp;&nbsp; workshop/conference organization.<o:p></o:p></spa=
n></p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal><span style=3D'font-size:10.0pt;font-family:"Courier N=
ew";
color:black'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal><span style=3D'font-size:10.0pt;font-family:"Courier N=
ew";
color:black'>Proposals are expected in ASCII or PDF format. All proposals
should be<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal><span style=3D'font-size:10.0pt;font-family:"Courier N=
ew";
color:black'>submitted to the Workshop Chair by email by February 10, 2012.=
<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal><span style=3D'font-size:10.0pt;font-family:"Courier N=
ew";
color:black'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal><span style=3D'font-size:10.0pt;font-family:"Courier N=
ew";
color:black'>Reviewing Process:<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal><span style=3D'font-size:10.0pt;font-family:"Courier N=
ew";
color:black'>=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D<o:p></o=
:p></span></p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal><span style=3D'font-size:10.0pt;font-family:"Courier N=
ew";
color:black'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal><span style=3D'font-size:10.0pt;font-family:"Courier N=
ew";
color:black'>Each submitted proposal will be reviewed by the Workshop Chair=
 and
the<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal><span style=3D'font-size:10.0pt;font-family:"Courier N=
ew";
color:black'>Conference Program Chairs. Proposals that appear well-organized
and<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal><span style=3D'font-size:10.0pt;font-family:"Courier N=
ew";
color:black'>that fit the goals and scope of ICLP will be selected.&nbsp; T=
he
decision<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal><span style=3D'font-size:10.0pt;font-family:"Courier N=
ew";
color:black'>will be notified by email to the responsible organizer by Febr=
uary
26,<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal><span style=3D'font-size:10.0pt;font-family:"Courier N=
ew";
color:black'>2012.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal><span style=3D'font-size:10.0pt;font-family:"Courier N=
ew";
color:black'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal><span style=3D'font-size:10.0pt;font-family:"Courier N=
ew";
color:black'>The definitive length of the workshop will be planned accordin=
g to
the<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal><span style=3D'font-size:10.0pt;font-family:"Courier N=
ew";
color:black'>number of submissions received by the different workshops. For
every<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal><span style=3D'font-size:10.0pt;font-family:"Courier N=
ew";
color:black'>accepted workshop, the ICLP local organizers will prepare a
meeting<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal><span style=3D'font-size:10.0pt;font-family:"Courier N=
ew";
color:black'>place and arrange the distribution of the workshop proceedings=
<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal><span style=3D'font-size:10.0pt;font-family:"Courier N=
ew";
color:black'>(usually on a pendrive). The proceedings, however, should be
produced<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal><span style=3D'font-size:10.0pt;font-family:"Courier N=
ew";
color:black'>by the workshop organizers. Any workshop registration fees wil=
l be<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal><span style=3D'font-size:10.0pt;font-family:"Courier N=
ew";
color:black'>handled together with the conference fees.<o:p></o:p></span></=
p>

